## 🗓 Study Plan Overview

| Week | Theme | Days |
|------|-------|------|
| Week 1 | Survival Basics | 1–7 |
| Week 2 | Conversations & Context | 8–14 |
| Week 3 | Deeper Conversations | 15–21 |
| Week 4 | Polish & Confidence | 22–30 |

Every 7th day includes a full checkpoint review and an 8-question mini-test.

